Polymetal Gains First Day in Four as Revenue Rises 59% on Output

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-10-13T09:49:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/polymetal-gains-first-day-in-four-as-revenue-rises-59-on-output.html
OAO Polymetal climbed for the first
day in four after the Russian silver and gold producer boosted
third-quarter revenue 59 percent as output and prices of both
metals rose.  The shares jumped as much as 2.5 percent and traded 0.8
percent higher at 471 rubles by 1:41 p.m. in Moscow.  Revenue climbed to $374 million from $235 million a year
earlier, Polymetal said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Corcoran at 
